        "definition": "Common collocations with \"view\"",
        "examples": [
          "View something as... — Consider something in a specific way",
          "Come into view — Become visible",
          "In view of... — Considering something",
          "View on/about/issue — Opinion about a topic",
          "In someone's view — According to someone's opinion",
          "Viewpoint / Point of view — Perspective or opinion"
        ]
      }
